System Requirements Specification (v1.0)
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~


- Installer:

  - Ada program using aShell to install a vanilla archLinux OS.
  

  
- Default archy setup:

  - Kernel              ~ Linux-lts
  - Filesystems         ~ Ext4 (root) and Zfs (/home and /laceOS) (consider Brtfs)

  - OS  package manager ~ Pacman/Pacaur/Pikaur/Custom Ada Gui
  - Ada package manager ~ Alire

  - Desktop             ~ Xfce4
  - Display Manager     ~ Xorg

  - System backup       ~ Timeshift
  - User backup         ~ ?

  - Media Player        ~ VLC
  - Bittorrent          ~ Transmission

  - Network             ~ NetworkManager
  - Firewall            ~ Uncomplicated Firewall (Gui)

  - Login Manager Gui   ~ ?



- Custom Ada applets:

  - Pacman/Pacaur/Pikaur Gui
  - System Settings Gui
  - Alire Gui
  
  
  
- Package Selection

  - Choose one/best of each application area.
  

  
- Customisation
  
  - Apply performance and security recommendations.